<plot>The film is a visual representation of the transmigration of the soul. Palingenesis originates from the Greek PALIN (again) and GENESIS (birth); a rebirth. In the tradition of classic German Expressionism of the 1920's, both visually and acoustically, the film is suggestive, haunting and suspenseful.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?421003</url></doc>
